*Predstavlja* se kao dečak sa dobrim manirima. (He presents himself as a boy with good manners.)
*Predstavljanje* njegovih ideja je inspirisalo svu ekipu. (The presentation of his ideas inspired the whole team.)
*Ona se *predstavila* kao nova članica tima. (She introduced herself as a new member of the team.)
*Predstavilo* se više od 50 inovativnih ideja. (More than 50 innovative ideas were presented.)